ChangeList.Description: Added the `RoleManagementPolicy.Read.AzureADGroup` delegated and application permissions to the read operations of the [privileged identity management (PIM) for groups APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagement-for-groups-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added the `RoleManagementPolicy.Read.AzureADGroup` delegated and application permissions to the read and write operations of the [privileged identity management (PIM) for groups APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagement-for-groups-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).
Added the **privilegedAccess** relationship to the [identityGovernance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupAssignmentSchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupAssignmentSchedule?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupAssignmentScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupAssignmentScheduleInstance?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupAssignmentScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupAssignmentScheduleRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupEligibilitySchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupEligibilitySchedule?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupEligibilityScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupEligibilityScheduleInstance?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupEligibilityScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupEligibilityScheduleRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the `RoleManagementAlert.Read.Directory` delegated and application permissions to the read operations of the [privileged identity management (PIM) for Azure AD Roles APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagementv3-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added the `RoleManagementAlert.ReadWrite.Directory` delegated and application permissions to the read and write operations of the [privileged identity management (PIM) for Azure AD Roles APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagementv3-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).
Added the **roleManagementAlerts** relationship to the [identityGovernance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [refresh](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/unifiedRoleManagementAlert-refresh?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [unifiedRoleManagementAlert](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleManagementAlert?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [refresh](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/unifiedRoleManagementAlert-refresh?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [unifiedRoleManagementAlert](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleManagementAlert?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [remediate](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/unifiedRoleManagementAlert-remediate?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [unifiedRoleManagementAlertIncident](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleManagementAlertIncident?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added support for the `RoleAssignmentSchedule.Read.Directory` application permission to the read operations of the [unifiedRoleAssignmentSchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleassignmentschedule?view=graph-rest-1.0),  [unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleassignmentscheduleinstance?view=graph-rest-1.0), and [unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleassignmentschedulerequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resources.

Added support for the `RoleEligibilitySchedule.Read.Directory` application permission to the read operations of the [unifiedRoleEligibilitySchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleeligibilityschedule?view=graph-rest-1.0),  [unifiedRoleEligibilityScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleeligibilityscheduleinstance?view=graph-rest-1.0), and  [unifiedRoleEligibilityScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleeligibilityschedulerequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resources.

Added support for the `RoleAssignmentSchedule.ReadWrite.Directory` application permission to the read and write operations of the [unifiedRoleAssignmentSchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleassignmentschedule?view=graph-rest-1.0),  [unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleassignmentscheduleinstance?view=graph-rest-1.0), and  [unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleassignmentschedulerequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resources.

Added support for the `RoleEligibilitySchedule.ReadWrite.Directory` application permission to the read and write operations of the [unifiedRoleEligibilitySchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleeligibilityschedule?view=graph-rest-1.0),  [unifiedRoleEligibilityScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleeligibilityscheduleinstance?view=graph-rest-1.0), and  [unifiedRoleEligibilityScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleeligibilityschedulerequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resources.
Added the **roleAssignmentScheduleRequests** relationship to the [rbacApplication](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/rbacapplication?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this resource and related methods to assign and manage active role assignments to a principal through Privileged Identity Management (PIM).
Added the **roleAssignmentSchedules** relationship to the [rbacApplication](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/rbacapplication?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [unifiedRoleAssignmentSchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleAssignmentSchedule?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this resource and related methods to identify the active role assignments in your tenant.
Added the **roleAssignmentScheduleInstances** relationship to the [rbacApplication](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/rbacapplication?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleInstance?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this resource and related methods to identify all instances of active role assignments in your tenant.

Added the [roleEligibilityScheduleRequests](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleAssignmentScheduleRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) relationship to the [rbacApplication](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/rbacapplication?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [unifiedRoleEligibilityScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleEligibilityScheduleRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this resource and related methods to assign and manage role eligibilities for principals through Privileged Identity Management (PIM).
Added the **roleEligibilitySchedules** relationship to the [rbacApplication](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/rbacapplication?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [unifiedRoleEligibilitySchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleEligibilitySchedule?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this resource and related methods to identify the assignments of role eligibilities in your tenant.
Added the **roleEligibilityScheduleInstances** relationship to the [rbacApplication](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/rbacapplication?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [unifiedRoleEligibilityScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleEligibilityScheduleInstance?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this resource and related methods to identify all instances of role eligibilities in your tenant.
Added the **roleManagementPolicies** relationship to the [policyRoot](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/policyroot?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [unifiedRoleManagementPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleManagementPolicy?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this resource and related methods to identify the policies and manage the associated rules and settings for Azure AD RBAC roles.
Added the **roleManagementPolicyAssignments** relationship to the [policyRoot](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/policyroot?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [unifiedRoleManagementPolicyAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRoleManagementPolicyAssignment?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this resource and related methods to identify the policies that are assigned to Azure AD RBAC roles, and their rules and settings.
Added the **privilegedAccess** relationship to the [identityGovernance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupAssignmentSchedule](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupAssignmentSchedule?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupEligibilityScheduleInstance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupEligibilityScheduleInstance?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the [privilegedAccessGroupEligibilityScheduleRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedAccessGroupEligibilityScheduleRequest?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods for governing membership and ownership of groups through PIM for groups.

Added the `PrivilegedEligibilitySchedule.Read.AzureADGroup` delegated and application permissions to the read operations of [privileged identity management (PIM) for groups APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagement-for-groups-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added the `PrivilegedEligibilitySchedule.ReadWrite.AzureADGroup` delegated and application permissions to the read and write operations of [privileged identity management (PIM) for groups APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagement-for-groups-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added the `PrivilegedAssignmentSchedule.Read.AzureADGroup` delegated and application permissions to the read operations of [privileged identity management (PIM) for groups APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagement-for-groups-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added the `PrivilegedAssignmentSchedule.ReadWrite.AzureADGroup` delegated and application permissions to the read and write operations of [privileged identity management (PIM) for groups APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagement-for-groups-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).

Removed the privilegedRole resource type and its associated methods. Use the [privileged identity management (PIM) iteration 3 APIs](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/privilegedidentitymanagementv3-overview?view=graph-rest-1.0) to manage Azure AD roles.
